// SourdoughPro — Secrets template.
//
// USAGE:
//   1. Copy this file to `Config/Secrets.xcconfig` (gitignored).
//   2. Paste your real key after the `=` sign.
//   3. Build & run — `Bundle.main.infoDictionary["OpenAIAPIKey"]` will resolve
//      to your key, and `OpenAIVisionService` will activate automatically.
//   4. NEVER commit `Secrets.xcconfig`. Only this `.template` is in git.
//
// You can have separate keys per configuration if you want
// (Debug vs. Release). For now, one key for both is fine.

// Strip the `sk-` prefix in the comment — your real key goes here:
OPENAI_API_KEY = REPLACE_ME_WITH_YOUR_OPENAI_KEY

// Xcode quirk: `//` inside an xcconfig value is treated as a comment.
// If your key ever contains `//`, escape it as `/${SLASH}/`. OpenAI keys don't.
